text: Ohinewai of ÅŒhinewai is a small town in the Waikato District, New Zealand. It is situated of the east bank of the Waikato River and is 9 kilometers north of Huntly on State Highway 1. In 2019 bed manufacturer Comfort Group announced its intention to create housing estate. It has a primary school in the town. ==References== Category:Towns in Waikato
